programme.title: Blood And Bone
programme.desc: Isaiah Bone (Michael Jai White) ar en skicklig mastare i kampsport. Efter fem år bakom galler skall han nu ut i verkligheten och borja ett nytt liv. Han anlander till Los Angeles dar ingen vet vem han ar och dar overraskar han alla genom att slåss som en varldsmastare. På gatorna i LA ar det gangsterkungen James som styr och Bone tar sig snart an utmaningen att forsoka storta honom. Men Bone doljer en mork hemlighet och han ar dessutom ute efter hamnd. Bone upptacker snart att han måste slåss for sitt liv. Allt står på spel! programme.desc: Polisen har misslyckats med att krossa ligan som svarar for den illegala spelverksamheten i Florida. Marinofficeren Johnny Firpo (Terence Hill) tar over uppdraget och raknar med hjalp av ex-spelaren Charlie Firpo (Bud Spencer). Det udda paret visar sig vara halvbroder, men Charlie vill andå inte hjalpa Johnny. Inte forran denne ljuger ihop en historia om att deras far ar blind och måste genomgå en dyr operation. Charlie inser att han måste tjana ihop till operationen genom ett antal poker- och spelvinster. Som vanligt får paret också många tillfallen att utnyttja sina stenhårda navar!

programme.title: The Fourth Musketeer
programme.desc: På uppdrag av sin far reser den unge dArtagnan från landsbygden i Gascogne till Paris, dar han blir indragen i en listig och mycket komplicerad komplott mellan kungens musketorer och kardinal Richelieus gardister. Blod ska spillas, och den som inte ar på sin vakt kommer få satta livet till.

programme.title: Jumper
programme.desc: Av regissoren till The Bourne Identity kommer annu en extrem adrenalinchock som tanjer på fantasins begransningar… David Rice ar en ung man utan granser – en “jumper” – fodd med den markliga formågan att kunna teleportera sig sjalv vart som helst på jorden inom ett ogonblick. Nar David upptacker att det finns fler som honom sjalv kastas han plotsligt in mitt i ett forntida krig. Han jagas av en blodtorstig skara fanatiker, fast beslutna att utrota alla jumpers. Nu måste David anvanda sin mycket speciella gåva smart for att ha en chans att overleva…

programme.title: Wild Target
programme.desc: En klumpig yrkesmordare blir foralskad i sitt offer och måste skydda henne från både sin egen organisation och polisen.

programme.title: Elektra
programme.desc: Marvels femme fatale; Elektra (Garner) bevisar att utseende kan doda nar den sexigaste actionhjalten någonsin bryter sig ut från serietidningssidorna till filmduken. I sitt nya uppdrag tvingas hon fatta ett odesdigert beslut i kampen mellan gott och ont!

programme.title: Survivor
programme.desc: Survivor ar en thriller om en av det amerikanska utrikesdepartementets sakerhetsexperter som får en tjanst vid USA:s ambassad i London. Hennes jobb ar att stoppa terrorister från att ta sig in i USA och det placerar henne direkt i skottlinjen. Dodshotad, oskyldigt brottsanklagad, vanhedrad och på flykt måste hon till varje pris komma på hur hon ska rentvå sig och samtidigt stoppa en omfattande terrorattack som ar planerad att aga rum under nyårsfirandet vid Times Square i New York.

programme.title: Texas Red
programme.desc: Den sanna historien om legendariske Texas Red, en afroamerikansk man som vildsint jagades utmed prariens sargade landskap av hundratals laglosa cowboys genom Mississippis vintervildmark. Allt for att lagga beslag på den hogst eftertraktade beloningen.

programme.title: Cold Zone
programme.desc: En storm ar på vag. Ingen kan forutsaga den. Ingen kan mata dess storlek. Nu måste en familj overleva den. Och ingen kan soka skydd från stormen, ingen kommer in från kylan…

programme.title: Joyride
programme.desc: Jon ar en forkrossad men andå charmig odugling i nastan allt han foretar sig, Luke ar en mastare på att kora bil och på flykt från sitt forflutna och Keira ar drive-thru-bitrade på ett burgerstalle och veganaktivist. Tillsammans bildar de tre en trio tillfalliga banditer nar de reser genom hela Nya Zeeland i en "lånad" gul Mini Cooper och ifrågasatter samhallets likriktning och jagar forlorad karlek med ett massivt polisuppbåd och varsta mediacirkusen hack i hal.

programme.title: Night of the Sicario
programme.desc: En transport av familjen till ett hogriskvittne blir attackerad och i skottvaxlingen skadas fadern svårt. Agenterna satta att skydda honom och dottern lyckas fora dem i sakerhet till ett narbelaget hus. Det visar sig vara ett aldreboende drivet av den mångforslagna Taylor Ward.

programme.title: Immortals
programme.desc: Efter att de grekiska krigarna till slut vunnit over Titanerna, dyker ett nytt hot upp mot dem. Med enorm kraft, deklarerar Kung Hyperon krig mot hela manskligheten. Med sin blodtorstiga och vansinniga arme soker Hyperion genom Grekland efter den legendariske Epirus båge, ett vapen med obeskrivlig kraft, som smidits i himlen av sjalvaste Ares sjalv. Om vapnet hamnar i kungens ago, kan det forgora hela manskligheten, till och med forinta gudarna. Men de forntida lagarna forbjuder gudarna att ingripa i manskliga konflikter och gudarna forblir maktlosa mot Hyperion och hans arme.

programme.title: Även anglar ater bonor
programme.desc: Fribrottaren Charlie (Bud Spencer) och drommaren Sonny (Giuliano Gemma) ar två fattiga tuffingar i 30-talets Chicago som hoppas på battre tider. De får chansen till stora pengar nar de borjar arbeta for en maffiaboss. Problemet ar att de ar alldeles for blodiga. De lånar ut pengar till fattiga istallet for att inkassera beskyddarpengar och driver hela tiden maffiabossen till vansinne. Till slut beslutar sig skurkarna for att undanroja Charlie och Sonny. Men de har glomt en sak - Charlies formidabla styrka sitter framst i navarna!

programme.title: Supersnutarna
programme.desc: De alskar fighter och planerar ett stort rån - och de ar filmnes hjaltar!Det har bara gått fem minuter av denna actionkomedi då Terence Hill och Bud Spencer redan forstort tre amerikanska vrålåk och spoat upp deras agare. Matt Kirby (Hill) och Wilbur Walsh (Spencer) ar två hårdslående bråkmakare, men med hjartat på ratta stallet. Efter ett misslyckat rånforsok i Miami hamnar de av misstag på stadens polisskola. Trots att de har svårt att skilja på ratt och fel klarar de utbildningen och utses till motorcykelpoliser. De gor sitt basta for att bli utsparkade ur poliskåren, men hur hårt de an anstranger sig går de ur varje fight som hjaltar!

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Fungi
programme.desc: Ett fartfyllt aventyr som staller vetenskap och naturlig balans mot kortsiktigt tankande i en kamp for mansklighetens overlevnad.

programme.title: Joyride
programme.desc: Jon ar en forkrossad men andå charmig odugling i nastan allt han foretar sig, Luke ar en mastare på att kora bil och på flykt från sitt forflutna och Keira ar drive-thru-bitrade på ett burgerstalle och veganaktivist. programme.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 3
programme.desc: Det hela borjar med att en magisk spira transporterar deras goda van April genom tid och rum, anda till samurajernas Japan. Leonardo och ganget ger sig genast av efter henne, och måste nu besegra den elake Lord Naringa for att radda den insparrade April och återta spiran som lorden kommit over. Annars lar de bli fast i medeltida Japan i eviga tider. Och dar finns ju inte ens några pizzerior…

programme.title: Salt And Fire
programme.desc: En forskare blir kidnappad och slangd ut i en dodsbringande oken dar hon måste kampa mot elementen for att overleva.

programme.title: Bulletproof Monk
programme.desc: The Monk ar en zen-cool martial arts-mastare vars uppgift har varit att beskydda en maktig antik skrift, en mystisk artefakt som bar nyckeln till obegransad makt. Nu har The Monk inlett sitt sokande efter skriftens naste vaktare, och uppdraget for honom till USA.

programme.title: Supersnooper
programme.desc: Terence Hill ar den nyutbildade polismannen Dave Speed, som ska inkassera en parkeringsbot mitt i ett olandigt traskområde. Tyvarr ar det också platsen for ett topphemligt atombombsprov. Dave får en rejal dos radioaktivitet, vilket ger honom overnaturliga krafter! Han klarar fall från hoga skyskrapor och flyttar saker med tankekraft. Daves kollega Willy (Ernest Borgnine) vagrar in i det langsta att inse att Dave verkligen har superkrafter - något som alla skurkar dock får kanna på.

programme.title: Daredevil
programme.desc: Mot DAREDEVIL - Marvels legendariske superhjalte, kand som Mannen utan fruktan. Med spektakulara specialeffekter, slagsmålsscener utver det vanliga och nonstop action. På dagtid arbetar den blinde Matt Murdock som advokat, på natten ar han DAREDEVIL. En maskerad hjalte som bevakar stadens morka grander.

programme.title: Ghost Rider - Spirit Of Vengeance
programme.desc: Eld ska med eld bekampas! Johnny Blaze kampar alltjamt mot sin forbannelse som djavulens prisjagare. Och nar en hemlig religios sekt vill anlita hans tjanster, kanner han sig inte redo att annu en gång iklada sig Ghost Riders brinnande krafter och makt. Men kanske ar detta den sista mojligheten att gora sig fri från djavulens forbannelse en gång for alla!

programme.title: Flight World War II
programme.desc: Fångad I en strid mellan Tyska och Allierade styrkor kampar passagerarna i en modern 757 jet for att overleva efter att deras gjort en tidsresa tillbaka till 1940. I deras stravan att overleva lyckas de påverka historien och utgången av Andra Varldskriget.

programme.title: Dragon Lord
programme.desc: Dragon och Bull fordriver tiden mestadels med att glida omkring och jaga tjejer. Speciellt en, som Dragon ar sarskilt fortjust i. Efter ett misslyckat forsok att skicka ett karleksbrev hamnar radarparet ovantat på taket till en kriminellt gangs hogkvarter. Ganget stjal dyrbara artefakter från stadens tempel for att smuggla vidare till giriga vasterlanningar, men Dragon och Bull kanner for forsta gången sin plikt, och bestammer sig for att ta sig an ganget.

programme.title: Supersnutarna
programme.desc: De alskar fighter och planerar ett stort rån - och de ar filmnes hjaltar!Det har bara gått fem minuter av denna actionkomedi då Terence Hill och Bud Spencer redan forstort tre amerikanska vrålåk och spoat upp deras agare. programme.title: The Villainess
programme.desc: Yrkesmordaren Sook-hee tar hamnd på de man som dodade hennes make. Efter att ha forlorat medvetandet vaknar hon upp hos den nationella sakerhetstjansten som vill att hon ska ta an sig topphemliga uppdrag. Sook-hee bestammer sig for att acceptera sin nya identitet som Yeon-soo for att hålla sig vid liv. Hon moter Hyun-soo och de borjar dromma om att starta en familj. Men på deras brollopsdag blir hon tilldelad ett uppdrag som kommer att forandra allt.

programme.title: American Exit
programme.desc: Charlie Bond står infor ett vagskal i livet. Han har nyligen separerat från sin fru och blir ombedd att ta hand om deras son Leo over helgen. Illa tajmat då han just ar i fard med att iscensatta en konstkupp for lite snabba pengar. Leo ar helt ovetandes om planen och bara ser fram emot att får spendera tid med sin efterlangtade pappa. Tatt inpå kommer verkligheten snabbt ikapp Charlie som nu ar i allra hogsta grad en jagad man av skoningslosa torpeder. Hans enda hopp ar att lyckats fly ut ur landet och att få återstalla sin relation till Leo som han vanskott i alla år.

programme.title: The Sudheide - Woods, meadows, open country
programme.desc: Forests and fields, moors and heathland, shepherds and sheep - these are the symbols of an ostensibly unspoilt landscape that has inspired poets and painters alike for centuries. The secret of the almost 500 km² nature reserve Naturpark Sudheide lies in its diversity: the origins of its soil, geology and topography can be traced back to the ice age. But the region between Hamburg and Hannover is anything but unspoilt. For centuries, it was synonymous with heathland farmers and formed as a North German cultivated landscape. This documentary tells of an almost unknown region, which has been strongly influenced by mankind for centuries, yet still remains diverse in its nature. Nature...

programme.title: Survival of the Fittest in the Alps
programme.desc: The documentary shows the survival strategies of various animal species in the high mountains of the Alps in winter. Despite freezing temperatures and limited food supply, chamois, red deer and snow hares manage to survive the cold months. Latest research reveals the amazing abilities the animals have developed to adapt to the extreme conditions and also how climate change is altering the behaviour of the alpine inhabitants.

programme.title: Secret Life Of Deer
programme.desc: 30 million white-tailed deer live in the United States. They have begun to adapt themselves to living in a world of traffic, pets and backyards. In Cayuga Heights, New York, the suburb’s residents are trying to get used to this exceptional living arrangement. The deer can be spotted daily from kitchen windows and porches. Life in the suburbs is deer heaven – large areas of grass, no predators and plenty of water means their population is on a steady rise. In this documentary, white-tailed deer are outfitted with special cameras to take the viewer into their world. Deercam allows us to see them in a new light – not frozen in the headlights of a car or as shy residents of the woods, but...

programme.title: Strandwolf
programme.desc: She moves through the seal colony on Namibia’s wild Skeleton Coast with purpose and focus, gingerly stepping around the adults who snap at her heels. She’s searching for smaller prey. Following her is a young German field scientist, Ingrid Wiesel, who has now spent 17 years with Tosca’s clan; tracking, observing, and learning everything she can about one of the world’s least understood and most unusual predators.

programme.title: King of the Mountains - Golden Eagle
programme.desc: Aerial shots of mating Golden eagles, a clash between a Golden and a White-tailed eagle, and an intimate glimpse into their nesting grounds combine to create a spectacular film. Tracking these majestic birds reveals the wild nature of their hunting grounds, showcasing the diverse animal and plant life that share their habitat with the king of the skies. Viewers are brought up close as the eagle effortlessly glides over forests and canyons, abruptly diving in a breathtaking pursuit of prey. Witnessing these birds in their natural habitats is witnessing them at their finest. Embark on a magnificent journey through the skies and landscapes with us.

programme.title: King of the Seas - Sea Eagle
programme.desc: The times where eagles have been seen as varmints are over. They are now perceived as an integral part of the food cycle. Due to the fact that the habitats of the sea eagles in Germany are largely found in the north-eastern regions that are rich in water, the movie accompanies the eagles to an island, home to hundreds of sea ravens, where they rob the baby sea ravens of their food. They seem to always profit from the successes of the fellow creatures in their habitats. This film introduces you to the expert poachers of the animal kingdom.

programme.title: Leap Of The Lynx
programme.desc: On the Iberian Peninsula, primeval landscapes are practically non-existent, so the Iberian lynx has lived on cultivated land for centuries – cattle, horse and pig pastures, cork oak forests, timberland, and even holy sites of pilgrimage. The diversity and beauty of these locations are truly stunning and their character and history as relevant to this story as that of the big cat itself. Until five years ago, both populations of Iberian lynx were quickly fading away. Their fragmented habitats were shrinking even further, they were starved by lack of prey and reduced by epidemics. But now, local authorities, scientists, landowners, and other groups have finally begun to act in unison.

programme.title: Bear Essentials
programme.desc: We follow three young bears of different species – polar bears, brown bears and sloth bears (like Baloo, the Jungle Book Bear) – that inhabit dramatically varied landscapes as they find their way in the world. We look at how their mothers teach them the skills they need to survive and watch the many dangers they face. Their young lives are full of learning, moments of great tenderness and life-threatening drama. Over three years all of our bears, despite hardships and losses along the way, prove they have what it takes, they all have learned their bear essentials.

programme.title: Wild Moments
programme.sub-title: S01 : E02 Wild Moments: Dangerous and Deadly I
programme.desc: Wildlife film-makers often risk life and limb trying to capture unique images of their dangerous protagonists. In Alaska a cunning grizzly threatens the son of Andreas Kieling, on the remote Wrangel Island in northern-east Siberia his colleague Uwe Anders is taken by surprise by a a polar bear, and off the coast of South Africa a diving-team is unexpectedly surrounded by white sharks. But the life of the film-makers is also threatened by elemental forces, life-threatening diseases and failing technical equipment: Deep in the vast rainforests of West Africa cameraman Klaus Scheurich nearly dies of malaria, and in South India a film team narrowly escapes death in a hot-air balloon accident....

programme.title: Wild Moments
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Wild Moments: Dangerous and Deadly II
programme.desc: Wildlife filmmakers often risk life and limb trying to capture unique images of their dangerous protagonists. A cunning grizzly grabs a salmon off Andreas Kielings fishing rod, in the depths of the Amazon River a diving team has a spooky encounter with piranhas, in the Mediterranean Sea the currents nearly push Thomas Behrend into the mouths of angry sperm whales defending a newborn - and cameramen who want to film jaguars in the dense jungle of South America become easy prey for the well camouflaged cats. The life of the film-makers is also threatened by elemental forces and failing technical equipment: In the swamps of North Australia violent storms hold up the crossing of tearing...

programme.title: Wild Moments
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Wild Moments: Dangerous and Deadly III
programme.desc: Wildlife filmmakers often risk life and limb trying to capture unique images of their dangerous protagonists. In the Kruger National Park Josef Jozefowicz steps into a lionesses den to film her cubs, in Alaska Andreas Kieling mingles with giant elk bulls in order to film them in action, and in Florida his colleague Zoltan Torok gets very close to an alligator mother guarding its nest. programme.title: Moksgmol - The Quest for the Spirit Bear
programme.desc: A forest that lives off fish, a white bear that is not a polar bear, and wolves that feed off the ocean… Canada’s Great Bear Rain Forest is a strange and pristine world, a land that time almost forgot. The awe-inspiring northern coastline of British Columbia with its great fjords that rival those in Norway, is the habitat of numerous species and the scene for the amazing co-existence of wolves, ravens, salmon, bears and a mystical rainforest, whose lives are intricately intertwined…

programme.title: The Moose Detective
programme.desc: Moose are an iconic species and of great importance to Sweden. That is why the country counts on a very special expert - the moose detective. Recently, a problem has developed on Öland regarding its moose. For a few years now on the island, the moose calves have been dying shortly after birth. Its a mystery. Every effort is made to save them. The island has called upon the moose detective to investigate. He follows several leads. Soon one of the suspects is identified - climate change. But it is not easy to convict the culprit. There are other suspects as well, the food shortage for example. Maybe they have joined hands as accomplices. In Sweden moose are very important. They are game...

programme.title: Search for the Ghost Bears
programme.desc: Our film journey begins in Alaskas west. We are hoping to find glacier bears in the glacial regions of the Katmai National Park on the Douglas River. At the end of July, brown bears have now arrived to fish for salmon. In the surrounding forests, grizzlies look for berries and fresh, green twigs. The Katmai is Alaskas most volcanic area, and with 15 active volcanoes it is a veritable powder keg, surrounded by glaciers. In the Hook glacier region moose and lynx accompany us. Bald eagles have arrived at the glacial boundary and begin to tear apart their freshly caught prey. At last, we catch sight of a glacier bear. Hungry, he has left the ice region and has been forced down here in...

programme.title: A Winters Tale - The Journey of the Snowy Owls
programme.desc: Snowy owls live a life full of mystery up in the Arctic. Thousands of years ago, they built a community of fate with their neighbors – lemmings. About every four years, lemmings proliferate in huge numbers. This way, snowy owls have enough feed for their young. The owls lay up to eleven eggs and can successfully raise the chicks – each of them needs two to four lemmings per day. Lately, however, lemmings’ mass reproduction hasn’t been as regular in some parts of the Tundra. What will happen to them and the snowy owls? What is the ecological link here? And what will happen if one year the winter arrives way too early? The best way for many birds to adapt to the winter is to flee to the...

programme.title: Italys Uncharted Islands
programme.desc: Far from the glamour and spotlight of Lampedusa, Pantelleria is one of the best kept secrets among the Italian islands. Located closer to Tunisia than to the Italian mainland, Pantelleria closer to Tunisia than to the Italian mainland, Pantelleria has been nicknamed "The Last Island," a title also given by Giosuè Calaciura gave to his 2016 historical novel set on Pantelleria. Pantelleria, that is the island of lava, capers and of the liqueur wine that comes here Zibibbo. An island with an ancient history, where for centuries farmers and fishermen have pursued their craft. their craft. programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On February 23th 2017, policemen are alerted of the disapearrance of Brigitte Troadec, her husband Pascal, and their children Sebastien and Charlotte.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A Night of Horror at Devils Plateau (Marie-Jeanne Meyer Case) - On June 18, 2011, Marie-Jeanne Meyer, 17-years old, waved goodbye to her little sister before leaving for her daily jog on the heights of Tournon in Ardèche. She never came back. Three days later, her mutilated body was found in a freshly dug pit, near an area known to be cursed, "The Devils Plateau." Whats more, the crime scene looked like a mystical ritual ... Was it a ritual murder? Revenge? An unfortunate encounter? ...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A Mysterious Murder at the Farm (Valerie Bary Case)- On Friday, March 26, 2004, in the region of Dijon, Laurent Bary came home from his work to discover the lifeless body of his wife, Valerie, bathing in a pool of blood. According to the investigators initial findings, the 38-year-old nurses aid had been stabbed several times, seeming to validate the theory of a robbery gone wrong.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: On July 13, 2011, two boaters retrieved a suitcase that was floating in the bay of Lorient. Inside, they discovered the tied up corpse of a man.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Bloody Christmas next to the Leman lake (CASE OF RUTH LÉGERET) - On January 4, 2006, Ruth Legeret was found dead in the middle of a pool of blood at her luxurious property in Vevey, Switzerland. Next to her was the lifeless body of her friend, Marina Studer. Who could have killed these two simple and wealthy widows? Clue after clue, the Swiss polices investigation would revolve around an environment of family jealousy and financial greed.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: September 16 2005. The lifeless body of Audrey Jouannet, 24, is found hidden under the bed in her small apartment in Soisy-sur-Seine. It soon becomes apparent that the young woman has been tortured at length before being strangled. But surprisingly, though the highly meticulous murderer has taken care to leave no sign of his passage, the autopsy reveals traces of sperm on the victim. It will take all of the investigators intuition to pierce the mystery of this heinous crime...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Sylvain Dromard finds the body of his wife Laurence lying in a pool of blood in the kitchen. The crime was particularly violent and the theory of a burglary that went wrong is soon excluded. But investigators dont understand who could want the adorable hairdresser of Saint-Martin-dAblois dead. During the investigation, the work of profilers will enable them to draw a very precise portrait of the murderer...

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: After an ordinary dinner, Pierre and Gabrielle Labrell suffer severe abdominal pains.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Nelly Cremel, 39, leaves her home to go jogging... never to return. Eight days later, after a vast search campaign, her body is found. Theres no doubt that its murder. The case soon ignites public opinion, even inflaming passions at the highest level of the state. The clues lead investigators on a number of trails, from the shadows of the French secret service to a manhunt for a possible sex maniac, in a case of murder most foul.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: Willy Pomonti, a retired architect, is found savagely murdered in his opulent villa in La Celle-Saint-Cloud, near Paris. It soon becomes clear that the man has been tortured prior to death. At several points during this extraordinary enquiry, police will feel theyre holding the culprit... It will take them ten years to finally shed light on this particularly violent crime.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The lifeless body of Christophe Lejard is found by his son just metres from their home. The man was shot in the head as he was getting into his car to go to work. A veritable execution, which at first glance doesnt square with the profile of the quiet family man. Yet behind the appearances, the investigation gradually reveals all the hate and resentment that revolved around the victim.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: A man walks into a gendarmerie near Saint-Malo to report that his wife has been missing since the previous day. The couple are going through a divorce, but this mother would never have left her seven children alone! An extensive search is undertaken but the woman cannot be found. What has happened to Adeline Piet? The investigation spans several years and experiences many twists.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers
programme.desc: The corpse of Priscillia Ciatti, 14, is discovered by the side of a field, a few hundred metres from her family home. She never came back. Three days later, her mutilated body was found in a freshly dug pit, near an area known to be cursed, "The Devils Plateau." Whats more, the crime scene looked like a mystical ritual ... Was it a ritual murder? Revenge? An unfortunate encounter? ...

According to the investigators initial findings, the 38-year-old nurses aid had been stabbed several times, seeming to validate the theory of a robbery gone wrong.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers

Next to her was the lifeless body of her friend, Marina Studer. Who could have killed these two simple and wealthy widows? Clue after clue, the Swiss polices investigation would revolve around an environment of family jealousy and financial greed.

programme.title: Crime Scene Solvers

It will take all of the investigators intuition to pierce the mystery of this heinous crime...

programme.desc: A ballistic missile test by India recently shot down one of its own communications satellites.

programme.title: Mars InSight: Seven Minutes to Touchdown
programme.desc: The fate of the Mars InSight lander will all come down to a fiery seven-minute freefall into the Red Planet. Will it survive?

programme.title: Exoplanets
programme.desc: NASA may have just gotten one step closer to answering the question: are we alone? The Spitzer Telescope has made a groundbreaking discovery of exoplanets.

programme.title: Cassini: The Grand Finale
programme.desc: Twenty years after its launch, we bid farewell to the Cassini spacecraft as it plunges into Saturn’s atmosphere in a planned death spiral.

programme.title: Asteroids, Comets, and Meteors
programme.desc: How do these objects differ from one another, if at all? Nick Moskovitz, an astronomer at the Lowell Observatory, compares these two space solar system bodies.

programme.title: New Horizons: The Kuiper Belt Target
programme.desc: The New Horizons spacecraft revolutionized our understanding of the solar system as it rocketed past Pluto. Now, the craft approaches its next target…Ultima Thule.

programme.title: Direct From An Asteroid
programme.desc: The Hayabusa2 spacecraft has just completed one of the most intricate procedures in space exploration.

programme.title: The First Picture of a Black Hole
programme.desc: For the first time, scientists have captured a photograph of a black hole.

programme.title: Touching the Sun
programme.desc: NASAs Parker Probe Plus is on a mission to learn more about the Sun -- flying through dangerous radiation to become the closest spaceship to orbit our Sun.

programme.title: Private Moonshot
programme.desc: A non-profit organization established in 2011 is aiming to land the first Israeli spacecraft on the Moon. This is the story of their attempt and the excitement of being the first private company to have a spacecraft launched with the intention of going to and landing on the moon.

programme.title: Modern Day Killer Asteroid
programme.desc: 66 million years ago, an asteroid slammed into Mexico’s Yucatán Peninsula, causing a dinosaur mass extinction. Whats in store for humanity if it happens again?

programme.title: Camp X-Ray
programme.desc: Kristen Stewart spelar huvudrollen i Peter Sattlers hyllade debutfilm Camp X-Ray. Hon spelar Amy Cole, en ung kvinna som tar varvning i amerikanska militaren i tron att hon kommer att skickas till Irak eller Afghanistan. Istallet blir hon stationerad som vakt på ett okant militarfangelse, med tuffa villkor for såval basens fångar som de få kvinnliga militarer som arbetar dar.

programme.title: In Tranzit
programme.desc: Baserad på en sann historia. I chockvågorna efter andra varldskriget, under den kalla vintern 1946, skickas av misstag en grupp tyska krigsfångar till ett ryskt kvinnofånglager som styrs av kvinnliga fångvaktare. Fångvaktarna, som forlorat många narstående på grund av Nazisternas brutalitet, mottar de nyanlanda fångarna med stor fientlighet och ser en mojlighet till hamnd...

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Runaway Jury
programme.desc: Från mastaren John Grisham kommer en thriller med Dustin Hoffman, Gene Hackman, John Cusack och Rachel Weisz. En jury-fixare spelar ett dodligt katt-och-råtta-spel med en jurymedlem och en mystisk framling som båda erbjuder att "leverera" domen till hogstbjudande. Snart står både liv och miljoner på spel i en pulshojare full av ovantade vandningar.

programme.title: Griffin and Phoenix
programme.desc: Nar Griffin har fått diagnosen att han har dodlig cancer bestammer han sig for att ta livet i egna hander och ha lite kul innan han dor. Samtidigt som tiden for hans liv rinner ut traffar han och blir kar i Phoenix - som också har en hemlighet.

programme.title: Fast Girls
programme.desc: Nar kaxiga och gatsmarta Shania (Lenora Crichlow) traffar den ambitiosa medelklasstjejen Lisa (Lily James) kolliderar deras två varldar på loparbanan med explosiva foljder. De två sprintertjejerna kampar for att kvala in till VM i friidrott och moter tuffa motgångar och bitter rivalitet på sin dramatiska, hjartevarmande och inspirerande resa.

programme.title: The Good Heart
programme.desc: Jaques (Brian Cox – THE BOURNE IDENTITY) ager en sjaskig bar, som fungerar som ett andra hem for en brokig skara professionella drinkare. Jaques sjalv ar fast besluten att supa och roka sig till dods. Nar han moter den unge hemlose Lucas (Paul Dano – THERE WILL BE BLOOD), som också gett upp hoppet om livet, tycker han sig ha hittat den perfekte arvingen till baren. Jaques borjar lara Lucas sitt kungadomes manschauvernistiska lagar: inga nya kunder, ingen personlig kontakt med gasterna, och absolut inga kvinnor! Lucas lar sig fort, men vanskapen satts på prov då den olyckliga och vackra April (Isild Le Besco) soker skydd i baren.

programme.title: Finding Altamira
programme.desc: År 1879 upptacker den spanska arkeologen Marcelino till synes omojliga målningar i en dold grotta. Han inser snart att konsten måste vara 10 000 år gammal, men den katolska kyrkan ser påståendet som en attack på den bibliska sanningen.

programme.title: Secrets and Lies
programme.desc: Eftersom Hortense ar svart blir hon forstås forundrad nar hon får reda på att hennes biologiska mor ar en vit arbetarklasskvinna på vag allt langre ut i den samhalleliga periferin. Upptackten av sin nya familj forandrar Hortense, och att låta sig involveras i deras liv forandrar hennes likaval.

programme.title: Boys on the Side
programme.desc: Tre kvinnor begår av misstag ett brott och tvingas på flykt i denna komedi. Under resans gång utveckla något de aldrig riktigt kant tidigare: en kansla av tillhorighet och vanskap.

programme.title: Tillbaka till Yorkshire
programme.desc: Arthur Morrison får reda på att han har cancer och att han bara har några veckor kvar att leva. Hans vuxna son Blake reser till Yorkshire for att bo hos sin mamma i byn dar han vaxte upp. Nar Arthurs tillstånd forvarras ser Blake tillbaka på sitt forhållande med pappan. Han minns saker de gjort tillsammans, fortroligheten mellan dem och aven de forbistringar de haft. Nar fadern dor borjar Morrison fundera kring det band de haft. Han ger tydligt uttryck for motsattningar, frustration, karlek och forlust som alla ar delar i det komplicerade forhållande som finns mellan en far och hans son.

programme.title: Candy
programme.desc: Heath Ledger ar den hoppfulla poeten Dan som hals over huvud foralskar sig i konstnaren Candy (Abbie Cornish). Dan ar heroinmissbrukare, men Candy ar fascinerad och dras till honom. Tillsammans beger de sig ut på ostadig mark, sammanbundna av deras vansinniga karlek och glupska sexuella aptit. Med hjalp av universitetsprofessorn Casper (Geoffrey Rush), som kan skaffa dem pengar och få gratis droger, inleder de båda bohemerna en farlig flort med doden.

programme.title: Once Were Warriors
programme.desc: Hos familjen Heke finns ingen frid att tala om. Jake Heke blir våldsam nar han dricker, den ena sonen har gått med i ett gatugang och den andra står infor åtal. Mamman Beth och barnen står infor det svåra, men livsavgorande valet mellan att stanna kvar i en hopplos situation, och att slå sig fria. Once Were Warriors ar ett prisvinnande familjedrama om att bejaka sitt forflutna for att skapa sin framtid.

programme.title: Black Coal, Thin Ice
programme.desc: På en kolfabrik liksom vid en soptipp, i olika andar av provinsen Heilongjian, påtraffas delar från samma kropp. En man har styckats och spridits ut, på ett avstånd for stort for en ensam garningsman. Zhang Zili (spelad av Liao Fan, som belonades for basta skådespelarinsats i Berlin) åtar sig fallet, men under ett misslyckat ingripande blir två av hans kollegor skjutna och Zhang tvingas lamna sin tjanst. Fem år senare blir Zhang uppsokt av sin forne kollega. Ett dubbelmord, identiskt med det som agde rum 1999, har skett och Zhang får chansen till återupprattelse.

programme.title: This is England
programme.desc: Filmen utspelar sig i 80-talets England nar fler soldater skickas till Falklandskriget och nationalistiska krafter får fotfaste hos en arbetarklass utan arbete. Detta ar också tiden nar Ska och Oi-punk-kulturens gangbildningar snart blir uppdelade i musikfanatiker vs. skinnskallar. Mittemellan hamnar den 12-årige Shaun, som finner gemenskap i uniformen och brodraskapet som skinnhuvudena erbjuder.

programme.title: Ljus i skymningen (Lights in the Dusk)
programme.desc: Aki Kaurismakis film om nattvakten Koistinen som forlorar jobbet, friheten och drommarna. Men till sist skonjer han en strimma hopp.

programme.title: Gringa
programme.desc: En olycklig tonårstjej rymmer till Mexiko for att hitta den pappa hon aldrig kant. Tillsammans lar de sig att en familj kan bli hel igen, aven om de bara har de bitar som saknas.

programme.title: Fast Girls
programme.desc: Nar kaxiga och gatsmarta Shania (Lenora Crichlow) traffar den ambitiosa medelklasstjejen Lisa (Lily James) kolliderar deras två varldar på loparbanan med explosiva foljder. programme.title: Dont Come Knocking
programme.desc: Hollywoodstjarnan Howard Spence (Sam Shepard) har sett battre dagar. Han vilar på sina lagrar och lever på sin gamla stjarnstatus. Efter ytterligare en natt med vilda utsvavningar flyr han från inspelningen av nasta vasternfilm och rider ut på prarien och de stora vidderna precis som en av hjaltarna som han så ofta har gestaltat. Han soker tillflykt hemma hos sin mamma (Eva Marie Saint) som han inte har traffat på många år. Men inte ens dar stannar han sarskilt lange, for han får veta att han någonstans kan ha en son som han inte visste fanns. For Howard kanns det som en strimma hopp och ett bevis for att inte har levt sitt liv forgaves.

programme.title: Rules Dont Apply
programme.desc: I Hollywood 1958 uppstår attraktion mellan en skådespelerska (Lily Collins) och hennes chauffor (Alden Ehrenreich), vilket satter deras religiosa varderingar på prov och går stick i stav med chefen Howard Hughes (Warren Beatty) forbud mot deras relation. Rules Don’t Apply (baserad på en berattelse av Beatty och Bo Goldman) ar regisserad av Beatty och i rollistan ser vi stjarnor som Annette Bening och Matthew Broderick.

Som ensamstående mamma till en åttaåring kanns expeditionen an mer kravande, och med lika delar skuld och mod forsoker hon hitta balans i sin roll som banbrytare och mamma.

programme.title: Undergods
programme.desc: En sci-fi-dystopi kryddad med svart humor om en varld med endast ett fåtal overlevande, som alla ar en aning trasiga på sitt satt. Den kafkaliknande miljon kombinerad med 2020-talets krossade drommar ger redan i sig tittaren gåshud. Filmen borjar med att två liksamlare går runt langs de odelagda gatorna och vid sidan av arbetet berattar om sina grusade drommar som drivit dem till det dystra nulaget.

I terapigruppen for sexmissbrukare traffas också frisoren Dede (Pink) och norden Neil (Josh Gad) men det ar inte helt enkelt att vara van med någon av det motsatta konet nar sex har odelagt alla ens tidigare relationer.

programme.title: Fat Kid Rules The World
programme.desc: Troy Billings ar 17 år, overviktig och ska ta livet av sig. Precis nar han ska hoppa ut framfor en buss raddas han av Marcus, en charmig gatumusiker som har hoppat av high school. En skakig vanskap uppstår mellan de två killarna nar Marcus ber den fullstandigt omusikaliske Troy att bli trummis i ett nytt punkband. Troy tror att det hela mest ar på skoj, men i realiteten ar drivfjadern Marcus stora drom om att bli punkrockvarldens kung, med alla medel som kravs..

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
programme.desc: Vi tar igen vår skonhetssomn! Stanna kvar for mer prisvard underhållning utvald av Rakuten TV.

programme.title: Middle School: The Worst Years Of My Life
programme.desc: Rafe Khatchadorian har ett efternamn som ar svårt att uttala, hans fantasi ar rent episk och så har han en smula svårt for auktoriteter. Han ar mer engagerad grabb an rebellisk anarkist och ar nu på vag till sin senaste forsta skoldag på sin tredje hogstadieskola. Det ar ett sista chansen-skolbyte som hans hårt arbetande singelmorsa hoppas ska visa sig vara som klippt och skuret for Rafe. Men på Hills Village-skolan satts individualismen i skymundan genom skolans tyranniska uppforandekod.

programme.title: The Happytime Murders
programme.desc: I en varld dar "puppets" lever bland manniskor, men inte riktigt har uppnåt samma status, jobbar detektiv Phil (spelad av Bill Barretta). Han återforenas med sin forna partner, detektiv Connie Edwards (Melissa McCarthy) for att hitta den som mordade detektiv Phils bror och som nu ar ute efter flera ur casten till 80-talets succe-TV-serie The Happytime Gang. Phils gamla tjej (spelad av Elisabeth Banks) har utsatts for hot och ar nasta tilltankta offer. Snart pekar misstankarna mot Phil sjalv. Han sticker och måste nu ensam forsoka losa The happytime murders.

programme.title: Results
programme.desc: Personliga tranarna (Cobie Smulders och Guy Pearce) har i uppdrag att få deras nyrika och otroligt omotiverade klient (Kevin Corrigan) i form. Deras tre liv knyts snabbt samman både professionellt och personligen.

programme.title: 36 Husbands
programme.desc: 36 Husbands ar en mystisk, musikalisk, Kung Fu-spionkomedi med tre maktiga kvinnor – och ett gang akta man. Toppspionen och Kung Fu-mastaren Krista har speciella krafter och hon anvander dem for att få marschen mot ett tredje varldskrig att gå långsammare.

programme.title: 21 and Over
programme.desc: Jeff Chang ar universitetets basta student och hela familjens stora hopp. Men nar hans två basta kompisar ordnar en overraskningsfest åt honom nar han fyller 21 måste han valja. Ska han vara i form for medicintentan nasta morgon klockan åtta? Eller kasta sig handlost ut i den vildaste av natter med long drinks, lap dances, tjurridning, body tequilas, golf-cart-lopp, spyor, cross-dressing, slagsmål, partypinglor och fyllekorning? Vad skulle du sjalv valja?

programme.title: The Girl Next Door
programme.desc: Matthew Kidman (Emile Hirsch), en vanlig kille som går sista året på gymnasiet, blir kar i den nyinflyttade grannen Danielle (Elisha Cuthbert från TV-serien “24”), en sexig och snygg tjej som tycks ha allt. Snart får han veta att hon ar en mycket speciell tjej - Danielle har ett forflutet som fore detta porrstjarna. Matthew riskerar allt och får uppleva saker aldrig kunnat forestalla sig...

programme.title: I Heart Huckabees
programme.desc: Albert Markovski ar ledare for Open Spaces Coalition och han har upplevt en orovackande rad av sammantraffanden som han inte forstår inneborden av. Med hjalp av de två existentiella detektiverna Bernard och Vivian Jaffe undersoker Albert sitt liv, sina relationer och sin konflikt med Brad Stand, en foretagsledare som klattrar på karriarstegen på Huckabees, en popular varuhuskedja.

programme.title: Peace, Love and Misunderstanding
programme.desc: En komedi om en overspand New York advokat (Oscarsnominerade® Catherine Keener) som tar med sig sina två pigga tonåringar till hennes hippie mors (Oscarsbelonade® Jane Fonda) hus på landet for en familjesemester. Det var tankt att bli en avkopplande helgutflykt men som snabbt forvandlas till en sommar fylld med aventyr, romantik, musik, familjehemligheter och om att hitta sig sjalv.

programme.title: 10 Items or Less
programme.desc: Oscar och Golden Globevinnaren Morgan Freeman spelar har en filmstjarna som ger sig ut på rollforberedande research i ett snabbkop i ostra Los Angeles. Han moter en snabbtalande kassorska (Paz Vega) och de ger sig av på en gemensam resa for att visa varandra sina respektive varldar. Strandad utan vare sig mobiltelefon eller bil accepterar han tjejens erbjudande om att ge honom lift tillbaka till Beverly Hills. Under resans gång upptacker emellertid det har till synes omaka paret att de har vissa gemensamma namnare som for all framtid kommer att forandra deras syn på deras egna liv...

programme.title: Nurse Betty
programme.desc: Betty missar aldrig ett avsnitt av sin favoritsåpa A Reason to Love. Efter ett omvalvande mote med två mordare nar hon ser ett avsnitt forvandlas Betty till Syster Betty och ger sig ut på ett uppdrag for att hitta sin stora karlek doktor David Ravell. Folj Betty på hennes vilda och hysteriska resa over landet i sokandet efter hennes dromprins. Men kan Betty hitta honom innan mordaren hittar henne?

programme.title: Låt de doda vila
programme.desc: Jimmy ar inte bara en fan av heavy metal, skrack, och det ockulta. Han har ett mål: han vill kontakta sin avlidna mamma. Den nya killen i klassen, charmoren Amir, lockar Jimmy till att imponera skolans två snyggaste tjejer, Louise och Anna, med en liten rit. Efter riten inser Jimmy, att han har begått ett forfardligt misstag, som kan grava fram doda hemligheter och betyda hela jordens undergång.

programme.title: The Rules of Attraction - Lustans lagar
programme.desc: Jessica Biel, James Van Der Beek och Ian Somerhalder ger liv och skratt till den har arliga och skarpsinniga betraktelsen på sociala och sexuella forhållanden på college.

programme.title: MacGruber
programme.desc: Nar varldsfreden står på spel, nar terroristerna ligger på lur, nar varlden behover en superhjalte med hår som Hillary Clinton... vem kontaktar man då? MacGruber forstås! Enkrigsmaskin utan vapen som kan få ut ALLT av ett gem. En agent så hemlig att inte ensVI kanner till hans fornamn. En man som kvinnor vill vara och som man vill vara tillsammans med... eller ar det tvartom?

programme.title: Paper Man
programme.desc: Forfattaren Richard Dunne (JEFF BRIDGES) har en låtsaskompis som foljt honom sedan barnsben: superhjalten Captain Excellent (RYAN REYNOLDS). I ett forsok att återvinna sin forna storhet som forfattare, skickas han ivag till Cape Cod av sin fru Claire (LISA KUDROW) for att skriva sin andra roman. Men då Captain Excellent foljer med som kumpan och hejarklack blir livet dar inte riktigt som planerat... Den 17-åriga flickan Abby (EMMA STONE), vars tragiska forflutna har lett henne till att fly in i sina fantasier, ansluter sig till sallskapet, och en mycket speciell vanskap uppstår.

programme.title: Epic Movie
programme.desc: Dina favoriter från de basta Hollywoodfilmerna blir extremt roligt parodierade i denna galna komedi! Fyra foraldralosa och problemfyllda karaktarer (från fyra kanda filmer) blir fångna i en bisarr chokladfabrik. De lyckas så småningom fly till en magisk varld full med låtsas-snooch riktiga trollerier...

programme.title: Adult Life Skills
programme.desc: Anna har fastnat. Snart 30 men bor i sin mammas tradgårdsskjul, pratar knappt med någon, och agnar sin tid åt att gora kortfilmer med sina tummar som skådespelare. Något saknas, och det visar sig att Annas avskildhet ar hennes satt att hantera den stora sorg hon bar på. Men nar hon råkar bli kompis med en åttaårig cowboy borjar hon så sakteliga oppna upp sig... Adult Life Skills ar Rachel Tunnards forsta långfilm och berattar en lika delar sorglig och rolig berattelse om doden och att tvingas leva med den. Broadchurch-stjarnan Jodie Whittaker spelar den tillslutna Anna i en lika humoristisk som vacker rollgestaltning.

programme.title: Mama Weed
programme.desc: Nar en underbetald polistolk under ett tillslag upptacker att en av de involverade ar en person i hennes narhet tar hon ett livsavgorande beslut. Hon lyckas beslagta den massiva mangden hasch både polisen och den undre varlden vill åt, och med hennes erfarenheter i faltet och polisens resurser borjar hon sin egna kriminella verksamhet och sadlar om till knarklangare.

programme.title: A Haunted House
programme.desc: I denna skandalosa parodi på Paranormal Activity-filmerna hemsoks ett ungt par som precis flyttat in i sitt dromhem. Kort efter inflyttning upptacker de att de inte langre ar ensamma. Men det ar inte huset som ar hemsokt, det ar Malcolms flickvan. Malcolm hyr in allt från praster till Ghostbusters så att denna demon inte ska få forstora hans forhållande ... eller, annu viktigare, hans sexliv.

programme.desc: En valdigt modern blivande brudgum sager motvilligt ja till en svensexa med sina urbana kompisar i vastra Irlands vildmarker. Till gangets fasa får de sallskap av brudens oberaknelige bror, en alfahanne som kallas "Maskinen" och vars explosiva personlighet och vilda ledarskap tar med dem på en resa som de aldrig glommer.

programme.desc: Doug (David Tennant) och Abi (Rosamund Pike) ar två helt vanliga foraldrar med tre charmiga men valdigt excentriska barn. Nar det hårda foraldralivet hotar deras mentala halsa och aktenskap så bestammer de sig for att ta med barnen på en resa till Skottland till ett stort slaktkalas och for att halsa på Dougs minst sagt knappa pappa Gordie (Billy Connolly). programme.title: The Deadly Companions
programme.desc: An unholy alliance! Marking the feature film debut of one of Hollywoods most influential and widely referenced auteur directors, Sam Peckinpah, The Deadly Companions centers on a redemptive journey to escort a funeral procession through dangerous Indian Territory. Featuring fine work from a top-notch cast that includes the inimitable Maureen OHara at the height of her illustrious career, Peckinpahs first foray into film provides a promising glance into the energetic and violent nature of his iconic later works.

programme.title: Colorado Kid
programme.desc: Cowboy star Bob Steele (Valley of Hunted Men, The Trail Blazers) headlines this Poverty Row western drama. As the Colorado Kid, hes falsely arrested for murder and has to clear himself. The colorful cast includes Ernie Adams, Frank LaRue, and Horace Murphy, with direction by Sam Newfield (The Terror of Tiny Town, The Mad Monster).

programme.title: Lost Canyon
programme.desc: When Johnny Travers (Jay Kirby) is falsely accused of robbing a bank, its up to Hopalong Cassidy (William Boyd) to clear his name and find the real villains. Theres nothing better than watching Hoppy get rough with the rustlers, and its all the better when you get to hear the Sportsmen Quartette sing (I got Spurs) Jingle, Jangle, Jingle.

programme.title: Hawk of the Hills
programme.desc: A band of Indians led by the Hawk terrorizes prospectors in a valley. HAWK OF THE HILLS was originally released as a ten episode serial in 1927 but was re-edited into a five-reel feature (the version presented here) in 1929.

programme.title: Red Ryder: Ride, Ryder, Ride!
programme.desc: Red Ryder encounters bandits trying to hold up the stagecoach carrying the owner of the Devils Hole newspaper, Libby Brooks and her brother Gerry. Red successfully drives off the attackers but becomes embroiled in further conflict, leading to a duel that nearly claims his life.

programme.title: With Sitting Bull at the Spirit Lake Massacre
programme.desc: A long-thought-lost film finally surfaces after being unseen for over eight decades. Created and copyrighted by Sunset Productions in 1925 but not released until June 15, 1927, this silent epic features the superior Native American actor Chief Yowlachie (performing here under the name Chief Yowlache) as Sitting Bull. Other fine actors in the cast include the always popular Bryant Washburn and a young Bob Steele, who appears under his real name Bob Bradbury Jr. The story takes place in the 1860s or 1870s near Spirit Lake, Iowa. Settlements of whites are growing in that region but the Sioux Indians also have professed their interest in one such settlement. Chief Sitting Bull surveys the...

programme.title: The Two Gun Man
programme.desc: Ken Maynard stars in this vintage western about ranchers under threat from hired gunmen. Director Phil Rosen, whose career dated back to working with Thomas Edison and included several Charlie Chan features, keeps the action hot with help from a strong ensemble, including Charles King, Murdock MacQuarrie, and a horse named Tarzan! Maynard plays Blackie Weed, a marshall going undercover to capture and arrest some cattle rustlers.He finds himself up against some very bad men, and hes soon framed for murder. Watch as Blackie blazes his way to vindication with a .45 in either hand and the flame of righteous anger in his eyes... Kitty: Nita Martin. Joe Kearney: Lafe McKee. Lem Tolliver: Tom...

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat Gallagher and his sidekick Stoney Crockett are Secret Service agents in the Old West, dispatched by the government to investigate crimes threatening the young nation. In this episode, the G-Men are sent to the Ozarks to track down gold stolen from the U.S. Government. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan.

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: An outlaw gang is stealing gold from Chinese placer miners, then driving off their claims with outrageous taxes. Because theyre Chinese, they cant sue the local government agents. With Stoney posing as a Chinese miner and Pat pretending to be a representative of an Eastern engineering company, the U.S. government tries to bring an end to the careers of the outlaw gang and crooked state government agents.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.sub-title: S01 : E16 Bobbie Jo and the Beatnik
programme.desc: Bobbie Jo falls head over heals for an edgy young poet from New York. He likes her, too, but hes not fond of Hooterville. Of coure, Kate has to show Bobby Jo what this pompous fool is all about. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in 1963. Look for Dennis Hopper as the beatnik.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.sub-title: S01 : E17 My Daughter the Doctor
programme.desc: The family wants Billie Jo to become a doctor, but she wants to go to Hollywood to become an actress. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Directed by Jean Yarbrough. And be sure to look for Adam West in a pre-Batman role as Doctor Clayton Harris. Series created by Paul Henning. Episode first aired in January, 1964.

programme.title: Cisco Kid
programme.desc: A rancher is shot dead after discovering oil on his property. Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This weekly adventure series was a favorite of the 1950s, following two pals as they traveled the old west, righting wrongs and helping the underdog..The show was nominated for a PrimeTime Emmy Award in 1951 .It was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt. This episode aired in 1950.

programme.title: Cisco Kid
programme.desc: An ex-con is released from prison seeking vengeance against those who put him there. Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This weekly adventure series was a favorite of the 1950s, following two pals as they traveled the old west, righting wrongs and helping the underdog. The show was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt, and was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1951 This episode first aired in 1950.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Detectives Matt and Frankie face off with a murdering desperado who has been terrorizing the northwest. Starring Jim Davis and Mary Castle. Also starring Steve Brodie, RIchard Avonde, Helen Wallace, Gene Roth, and Edward Clark. Directed by William Witney. Episode first aired in 1954 .Produced by B movie veteran Edward J. White. Series won an Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.sub-title: S01 : E20 Wild Bunch of Wyoming
programme.desc: Matt and Frankie meet the Wild Bunch and their jovial leader Butch Cassidy.Starring Jim Davis and Mary Castle. Also starring Joe Sawyer, Slim Pickens, Lane Chandler, and Bob Carney. Directed by William Witney. Episode originally aired in 1954. Produced by B movie veteran Edward J. White. Series won an Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: While attempting to steal land from an Indian tribe, crooked ranchers kill one of the braves. The Judge must move fast to prevent an all-out massacre. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: In Family Ties, Judge Bean comes to the aid of the Peralta family as unscrupulous real estate agents try to force them off their land. Theyve learned that a railroad will need the property and they intend to make an undeserved profit. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.sub-title: S01 : E12 Annie and the Lily Maid
programme.desc: Choctaw looks to inherit the ranch of the murdered Sam Forbes, but Elaine, a previously unknown niece, appears, making Annie suspicious as the men fall for her seemingly delicate nature. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: Recently released from prison, Vic Carver, and his brother Johnny, searches for Annies Uncle Luke to enact revenge. Annie successfully gets her uncle out of town, but an angry Vic kidnaps Tagg. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy Award in 1955.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: Hawkeye and Chingachcook suspect that a young mans uncle is behind the recent attacks against him. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper.Episode originally aired in 1957.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: A man asserts that he has a Royal Grant that gives him ownership of the entire town.Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in November, 1957.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: Little Joes date, Jennifer, is abducted and held for ransom at the circus. He and Hoss search the circus for her, facing a tough crowd of carnies in their search.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: The Gay Cavalier
programme.desc: The Cisco Kid, along with Pancho, try to help an unhappy bride.

programme.title: Heart of the Golden West
programme.desc: Roy Rogers, Gabby Hayes, and Smiley Burnette team up to protect the ranchers of Cherokee City from the false charges of illegal cattle trafficking. It may seem like the odds are against Roy, but just watch as he changes the course of the law with his flaming bullets, and, of course, a few songs. For trivia buffs: Smiley Burnette joined Roy because Gene Autry, the actor for whom he usually served as a sidekick, had joined the service!

programme.title: Cowboy and the Senorita
programme.desc: Roy Rogers and Trigger get top billing in this one, while the senorita of the title, Dale Evans, is billed fourth. Maybe Dale needed a better agent! Then again, who pays attention to screen credits when you have such a funfilled fiesta of thrills and action? Roys most zestful musical adventure is about a worthless gold mine that turns out to have a hidden shaft filled with riches. But can Roy make the claim while hes trying to outrun a trumped up robbery charge? Its romance, rhythm, and revelry, all from Republic Pictures. Musical numbers include Bunk House Bugle Boy and Besame Mucho, plus the beautiful title song performed by Roy!

programme.title: Cowboy And The Prizefighter
programme.desc: Red Ryder takes Steve Stevenson, who has saved his life, to his ranch and gives him a job. Reds aunt, the Duchess, knew Steves father, who supposedly committed suicide after losing his ranch betting on a prizefight. Steve refuses to believe that his father took his own life, suspecting he was murdered. Red and Little Beaver aid Steve in finding his father killer.

programme.title: Daniel Boone, Trailblazer
programme.desc: Daniel Boone (Bruce Bennett) battles Shawnee warriors as he leads a band of settlers into Kentucky in this frontier potboiler from Albert C. Gannaway Productions. Made at the height of Hollywoods fascination with pioneer days, the film also stars Lon Chaney Jr. as Chief Blackfish, and country singer Faron Young as a handsome young suitor for Boones daughter. Theres plenty of action and danger here as the Shawnee are convinced that Boone is trying to steal their land. But Boone is ready, not even fearing death by tomahawk. It isnt how you die, Boone says. Its what you live for.

programme.title: The Lucky Texan
programme.desc: John Wayne stars in this vintage western. He and George Gabby Hayes strike it rich with a gold mine, only to find their lives complicated by women and crooked officials. Things get even messier when the good guys are framed for murder! Its all action here, particularly since legendary stuntman Yakima Cannut stars as one of the films heavies. Who will win the fight over the gold and the girl? Directed by Robert N. Bradbury for Monogram Pictures. Also starring Barbara Sheldon. (The film was also known as Gold Strike River.)

programme.title: Courageous Avenger
programme.desc: Gold, gangs, and the heroic fight for life! Johnny Mack Brown (Billy the Kid, Coquette) stars in this western thriller about murders going on in a mining community. Its a story full of twists, where the greed for gold is only surpassed by the struggle for life!

programme.title: Death Valley
programme.desc: A love story and a search for gold in the Valley of Death! Dubbed simple, powerful and dramatic by the New York Times on the date of its release, Death Valley is indeed an elegant depiction of love and deception in the American desert during the Gold Rush. In what was to be the final film of famed silent film director Paul Powell (Polyanna), a cast of mostly unknown actors produces uniformly excellent work. Lyrical and graceful, Powells film spins the tale of a young boy who finds love and gold, only to have it stolen from him.

programme.title: Outpost In Morocco
programme.desc: George Raft, Mary Windsor, and Akim Tamiroff star in this romantic drama from director Robert Florey (The Florentine Dagger, Daughter of Shanghai). Raft plays Capt. Gerard, a member of the Foreign Legion known for his romantic entanglements. Hes assigned to escort an emirs daughter to her fathers mountain citadel and learn about the emirs activities. Not surprisingly, Gerard finds trouble brewing! With footage shot in Morocco, this movie also features a beautiful musical score by twotime Oscar nominee Michel Michelet (Voice in the Wind).

programme.title: Born to Battle
programme.desc: Cyclone Tom Saunders starts a ruckus in a Chinese laundry and has to go before a judge. Unable to pay his fine, he is bailed out by a local cattle rancher and agrees to do 30 days work for him. Its not too long before he becomes enmeshed in a war between rustlers and outlaws.

programme.title: Brothers of the West
programme.desc: Tom Tyler plays Tom Wade, a range detective whose brother has been accused of robbery and murder. Wade has only one clue to prove his brothers innocence: a set of unusual tire tracks. This film was directed by Sam Katzman, who later became known as Jungle Sam for his association with a variety of jungle thrillers, and then as a master of all exploitation genres, from teen horror to flying saucer flicks!

programme.title: Fugitive of the Plains
programme.desc: In this continuation of the much loved Billy the Kid serials featuring dreamboat Buster Crabbe (perhaps best known for his numerous appearances as Flash Gordon in the 30s and 40s), Billy finds himself joining an outlaw band led by women in order to, once again, clear his name after being wrongly accused of a crime he did not commit. Helmed by famed B-movie director Sam Newfield, this film also features Al St. John, whose lovable Fuzzy character was as essential to the PRCs Billy the Kid series as Billy himself.

programme.title: Phantom Ranger
programme.desc: Cowboy hero Tim McCoy stars as Tim Hayes, a two-fisted G-Man working for the FBI on a counterfeit money case. The incredibly daring Hayes infiltrates a gang that has kidnapped a Treasury Department engraver. Under the direction of Poverty Row icon Sam Newfield, McCoy turns in another of his legendary slam-bang performances, making Phantom Ranger a perennial favorite of B-Western fans.

programme.title: Neath Canadian Skies
programme.desc: Its the mounties versus claim jumpers in this drama from Golden Gate Pictures. Based on an action-packed novel by James Oliver Curwood and directed by B. Reeves Maynard (Undersea Kingdom, The Phantom Empire), the film features an outstanding cast of Poverty Row regulars, including Russell Hayden, Inez Cooper, Cliff Nazarro, I. Stanford Jolley, and Kermit Maynard. For movie buffs: Cinematographer Marcel Le Picard began his career in the silent era and finished with exactly 200 credits!

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat and Stoney take time out from their duties to try and collect the bounty posted on a legendary golden wolf that roams the Colorado foothills. A couple of wolf hunters dont take kindly to a pair of amateur hunters horning in on their range and attempt to drive the G-Men away before they can capture or kill their quarry.

programme.title: Cowboy G-Men
programme.desc: Pat and Stoney travel to Wyoming to oversee a land opening and end up playing nursemaid to a pair of identical twin pranksters and a kooky Chinese cook. Meanwhile, a trio of outlaws are pursuing the twins seeking information they possess. Starring Russell Hayden, Jackie Coogan.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.desc: Billie Jo recieves an endowment, but instead of using it for medical school, she wishes to go to Hollywood.Kate meets with Judge Drucker to see if she can legally prevent the girl from goinng. Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Directed by Jean Yarbrough.

programme.title: Petticoat Junction
programme.sub-title: S01 : E19 Visit from a Big Star
programme.desc: A famous movie star (John Vivyan) stays at the Shady Rest Hotel. He wants to get away from the spotlight for a while, but it appears that Uncle Joe has told the entire valley that the hotel has a special guest. .Uncle Joe Carson: Edgar Buchanan. Betty Jo Bradley: Linda Henning. Kate Bradley: Bea Benaderet. Sam Drucker: Frank Cady. Also starring Pat Woodall and Jeannine Riley. Directed by Ralph Levy. Episode first aired January 28, 1964

programme.title: Cisco Kid
programme.desc: Cisco and Pancho work to uncover a cattle rustling operation.Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This weekly adventure series was a favorite of the 1950s, following two pals as they traveled the old west, righting wrongs and helping the underdog..The show was nominated for a PrimeTime Emmy Award in 1951. This episode aired in 1950. The show was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt.

programme.title: Cisco Kid
programme.desc: Cisco and Pancho investigate when a railway detective is found dead.Starring Duncan Renaldo as The Cisco Kid, and Leo Carillo as Pancho. This weekly adventure series was a favorite of the 1950s, following two pals as they traveled the old west, righting wrongs and helping the underdog. The show was produced by ZIV Television, the same company that gave us Highway Patrol and Sea Hunt, and was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1951 This episode first aired in 1950.

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Jim Davis stars as Matt Clark, a railroad detective who is investigating a railroad holdup. Starring Mary Castle. Directed by William Witney. Episode first aired in 1954.Produced by B movie veteran Edward J. White. Series won an Emmy in 1955. (This episode also features James Best (1926-2015), who would go on to appear on such shows as The Andy Griffith Show, Bonanza, and The Dukes of Hazzard.)

programme.title: Stories of the Century
programme.desc: Detective Matt Clark discovers the hideout of the famous Doolin gang. Clark, along with Detective Frankie, work to infiltrate the hideout and bring the Doolin gang to justice.Produced by B movie veteran Edward J. White. Directed by William Witney. Starring Jim Davis and Mary Castle, along with Leo Gordon, Joan Shawlee, Don Kennedy, Kenneth MacDoNald, Patrick Waltz, and Ken Chryson. First aired in 1954.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: In this episode, crooks posing as newspapermen attempt to blackmail a local rancher in order to steal his land and property. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery.

programme.title: Judge Roy Bean Collection
programme.desc: Judge Roy Bean endeavors to exact justice in the small town of Langtry in the Old West. Starring Edgar Buchanan, Jack Beutel, and Jackie Laughery. In this episode, Judge Bean discovers that a young vagabond he jailed for a minor offense may be involved in a major unsolved gold heist.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: With the help of Annie and Lofty, Clay Griffin, a lawman whose eyesight is deteriorating, confronts Johnny Storm and the Murdocks after they are involved in a robbery. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: Adventures of Annie Oakley
programme.desc: After raising money for charity with a circus sideshow, Annie and Tagg are robbed of their money by a man named the Welshman. Annie and Lofty set up a trap with one last performance. Annie Oakley: Gail Davis, Deputy Craig: Brad Johnson, Tagg Oakley: Jimmy Hawkins. This western adventure series aired from 1954-1957. Cowboy star Gene Autrey was an executive producer for the show, which was nominated for a Primetime Emmy in 1955.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: A town turns against Eben Cotten as he is accused of selling rifles to the Indians. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in December, 1957.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: An editor of a newspaper is framed for murder. Hawkeye: John Hart. Chingachcook: Lon Chaney Jr. This syndicated series was filmed in Toronto, and was the final project of prolific Hollywood director Sam Newfeild. Based on characters created by James Fenimore Cooper. Episode originally aired in December, 1957.

programme.title: Bonanza
programme.desc: Gunnar, a long-lost relative of the Cartwright family, arrives in Ponderosa, where the family takes him in for the night. Unknown to the Cartwrights, however, is Gunnars leading of The Comancheros, a dangerous band of criminals. After Little Joe and his girlfriend are kidnapped by The Comancheros, the Cartwrights and Gunnar must work things out.Starring Michael Landon as Joe, Dan Blocker as Hoss, Lorne Green as Ben, and Pernell Roberts as Adam. This beloved western drama ran for 14 seasons on NBC. Created by David Dortort.

programme.title: Under Western Stars
programme.desc: Roy Rogers debuts in his starring role as the likable cowboy sent to Congress with a mission: let Washington know about the suffering of farmers in the wake of Americas 1930s Dustbowl. Enjoy the singing cowboy in his first starring role, rubbing shoulder with politians, going up against greedy executives, and representing a whole people group youll see why Rogers became a national icon! Frog Millhouse: Smiley Burnett. Elanore Fairbanks: Carol Hughes. John Fairbanks: Guy Usher. Plus music and singing from the Maple City Four. (The song Dust was nominated for an Academy Award!) Directed by Joe Kane.

programme.title: Wagon Wheels
programme.desc: Randolph Scott (Ride the High Country) stars as Clint Belmet, the leader of a wagon train on the way to Oregon. Along the route he and his crew deal with various hardships, including Indian attacks and a fellow named Murdock (Monte Blue) who is out to stop them at any cost. With a cast that includes the likes of Gail Patrick and Billy Lee, this adventure saga was based on a novel by the western master, Zane Grey (Riders of the Purple Sage, Fighting Caravans). Trivia note: The films original title was Caravans West.

programme.title: In Old Cheyenne
programme.desc: Roy Rogers plays a newspaper reporter sent to Cheyenne to investigate a reputed troublemaker. While on the scene, he discovers who the real bad guys are, and sets out to right some wrongs. Also starring Roys usual sidekick George Gabby Hayes, plus Joan Woodbury, and George Rosener. This Republic Pictures western was helmed by director Joseph Kane (The Undersea Kingdom, Dakota) and features two musical numbers: Bonita and Linda Flor.

programme.title: The Last of the Mohicans
programme.desc: During the French and Indian War, Alice and Cora Munro are joined by Magua in the search for their father, a British officer. Little do they know, their father is being held captive by the Huron warriors, and Magua intends to betray them. Uncas, the last surviving warrior of the Mohican tribe and Hawkeye set out to rescue the hostages and the sisters before its too late.

programme.title: Northwest Trail
programme.desc: Mountie Matt OBrien assignment is simple: He is to escort the rather grouchy, and slightly annoying, Miss Katherine Owens to a remote outpost. Things complicate however when they arrive at the outpost and he stumbles upon an illegal mining operation. Stars include Bob Steele, Joan Woodbury, and Poodles Hanneford.

programme.title: Winds of the Wasteland
programme.desc: John Wayne stars in this Republic Pictures western about the final days of the Pony Express. Former rider John Blair (Wayne) enters a coach race to win a $25,000 government mail contract, but there are dozens of obstacles in his path. The rest of the cast includes Lane Chandler and Phyllis Fraser, plus Lew Kelly (Lady of Burlesque) doing a great comic turn as Rocky OBrien, the eccentric, self-proclaimed mayor of a deserted mining town.

programme.title: The Kansan
programme.desc: Richard Dix stars in this epic of the boisterous and brawling Old West! Wounded in a gun battle with the notorious James gang, John Bonniwell (Dix) wakes up in the hospital to find out hes been elected marshal! He quickly learns that this hot-headed frontier town can only be cooled off with blazing lead and dynamite! Jane Wyatt, Albert Dekker, Victor Jory, and Robert Armstrong also star in this tale of smashing fists and crashing bullets from director George Archainbaud (The Lost Squadron).

programme.title: Daughter of the West
programme.desc: A FLAMING PAGE FROM AMERICAN HISTORY Becomes a powerful motion picture...set against the panoramic grandeur of the West!. Martha Vickers stars as Lolita Moreno, a convent raised woman in the 1880s who learns about her Native American heritage through her relationship with an educated Navajo. Morena had been raised at a California mission, but when she leaves to teach school in Arizona, the threads of her mysterious past are revealed. This leads to her involvement with some dangerous people, and a chance to find love in the most unexpected way. The cast includes Phillip Reed, Donald Woods, William Farnum and Milton Kibbee. Pedro de Cordobaa stars as Chief Wykomas.

programme.title: Liza Marklund: Den Roda Vargen
programme.desc: Annika Bengtzon får i uppdrag att bevaka ett komplicerat mordfall dar offret ar en journalistkollega. Hennes efterforskningar får en ovantad vandning nar spåren leder till ett 40 år gammalt attentat på en flygbas i Luleå. Fler mord foljer, och medan Annika Bengtzon tranger djupare in i maktens korridorer verkar allt leda till att hon ar en seriemordare på spåren...

programme.title: Liza Marklund: En Plats I Solen
programme.desc: En kand svensk fore detta NHL-stjarna med familj hittas mordade i sitt hem i Marbella, och vallspressens Annika Bengtzon skickas till Spanien for att skriva om fallet. Solkustens morka baksida visar sig nar Annika kommer allt narmare sanningen - och det hela blir till ett smutsigt spel om droger, pengatvatt och brutal hamnd. Liza Marklund har med sina varldsberomda bocker om kriminalreportern Annika Bengtzon etablerat sig som en av Nordens absolut storsta deckardrottningar. En plats i solen ar den avslutande delen i en serie med sex filmer.

programme.title: Programmet fortsatter strax
